name: the Basics Premium / Luxury Tees
description:
Premium basics with variant colors and style, perfectly cut for him/hers.
Dressing well is often a product of getting the basics right, the things that most people don’t even notice, like T-shirts, chinos and denim.
 If they’re made properly, it’s these basics that make for a solid style foundation, and in this case, the only thing basic about them is the price.
